Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anypony heard from\NPinkie Pie since yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's\Nso important
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to meet her\Nhere this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia hasn't even\Nraised the sun yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everything's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're all here.\NThere's no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister Maud's\Ngoing to be here soon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need your help
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,taste-testing my\Nrock candy recipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we're happy to help\Nyou, Pinkie Pie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but this seems like an\Nawful lot of candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have gone a\Nteensy bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony ready for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My teeth hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've had plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And shouldn't you be on\Nyour way to pick up Maud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,from the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've only tried\Nhalf of the flavors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have to choose\Nthe perfect ones
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,before she gets here\Nso I have time to make more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud is your sister;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll love\Nyour rock candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm pretty sure\Nyou've made enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only staying\Nfor the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just\Nfor Maud, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making candy\Nfor all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of a very important,\Nsuper-duper special tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that only the closest and\Nbestest of friends can share.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make rock\Ncandy necklaces together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started when Maud and I{\i0}\N{\i1}were fillies on the Rock Farm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She taught me the Pie{\i0}\N{\i1}family rock candy recipe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has a secret ingredient.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's rocks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she showed me how{\i0}\N{\i1}to string the pieces{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to make them into a necklace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And once we were{\i0}\N{\i1}done, we'd trade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud and I have been trading\Nnecklaces back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,since I moved to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a sign that we'll\Nalways be best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, what a great tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The "secret\Ningredient" is rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are a special kind\Nof rock that Maud discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a rock are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Maud is heading off\Nto get her Rocktorate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in Rock Science,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this may be our last\Nchance to trade them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for\Nyou all to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that my best\NPonyville friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and my best sister friend are\Ngoing to become bestest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make bestestest friend\Nrock candy necklaces together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She expresses herself through\Nfashion just like Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's really smart and loves\Nreading, just like Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's honest and\Nloves forest things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and is good at games and...well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,SHE'S AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She sounds amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't she start worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,if you aren't at the train\Nstation when she gets here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope Maud\Nhas an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Never met a pony, or a\Ncritter, who didn't love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith's\Napple-spice muffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply cannot find\Nanything suitable to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt she'll notice\Nwhat anypony's wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The big deal is that it will be\Nvery difficult to show Maud
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what a strong fashion presence\Nwe have in Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if the most fashion-forward\Npony here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,can't keep her hat\Nfrom falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're all a little\Nnervous about Maud's visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Pinkie Pie's sister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's obvious Pinkie really\Nwants us to hit it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to make those rock\Ncandy necklaces together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is really important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everything\Nwill be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}WE'RE HERE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Maud?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you sure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not quite\Nas fast as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Gummy to stay with\Nher in case she got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she even moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,WE'RE OVER HERE, MAUD!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedimentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sedimentary rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really fascinating,\Nisn't it, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just so thrilled you\Ncould come for a visit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before your big trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie has told\Nus so much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Twilight and this is\NApplejack, Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, and Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ever so\Nglad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna\Nhave the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie tells me you\Nshare my love for fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really into expressing\Nmyself through my wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the delightful\Nfrock you're wearing now saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yes. Of course.\NI just meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. So this here's Winona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Owlowiscious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank, Opal, and Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie told us\Nyou have a pet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, You have a pocket pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a tiny mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a baby bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a trained butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the best,\Nmost awesome, funnest week ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for us all\Nto become bestest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud? Would ya care to\Ntry one of Granny Smith's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,famous apple spice muffins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, ha, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crunchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud's right. They\Nare crunchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, Pinkie Pie\Ntells us you like games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Boulder and I sometimes play a\Ngame called "camouflage."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of like\N"hide-and-seek,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but way more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly wish I had spent\Nmore time with Boulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm having a very\Nhard time remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like lookin' for\Na pebble in a haystack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, "in a pile\Nof pebbles."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to\Nmake it even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! I give\Nup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll hurt Maud's feelings\Nif we all stop playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, look how much\Nfun Pinkie Pie is having.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,IS THIS IT? IS THIS IT?\NIS THIS IT? IS THIS IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Found him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was hiding in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to interrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but we really should get these\Nlittle critters home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting awfully late and\Nthey've had a very busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud and I'd better\Nget going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to taste\Nthe rock candy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to use for our...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...best friends necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is different\Nfrom what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent all day\Ndigging in the dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was in her pocket\Nthe whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On the bright side, Boulder\Nseemed really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Maud was just nervous\Nabout meeting all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was just\Nacting a little "off"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because she's shy or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be awfully intimidating\Nto meet all of us at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,especially since we're\Nalready such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we spent some\Ntime with her one-on-one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to get to\Nknow her better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll be making those\Nbest-friend rock candy necklaces
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where shall we start?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen a few fabrics\NI think would be stunning with--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Choices, choices, choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you don't see\Nanything that speaks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to suggest--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie didn't tell\Nus you were so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, it's just, I\Nbelieve that is a dish towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it does go very\Nwell with your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I could\Nwork my magic
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn it into\Nsomething fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity and my sister\Nworking together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to design something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best day ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I could sew\Nall of these together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and make you something\Nyou would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Maud make\Nthe coolest scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there, Hummingway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ever so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He says hello, and he's\Nhappy to see us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could\Nspeak hummingbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hummmmm, hum, hum,\Nhum, hummmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These spiders only\Nlive in Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and even though they may\Nlook a teeny bit scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they're actually\Nvery sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and help keep other, more\Ndangerous insects away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at\Nthe rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Start thinking about which\Nflavors you want to put
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in your best-friend\Nrock candy necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure we're\Neven friends yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maud is a total bookworm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got lots of poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read anything\Nby Quill and Ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Flourish Prose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to read my own poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock. You are a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you are grey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like a rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've written thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so prolific!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This next one is about rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all about rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocks, these are my rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sediments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smooth and round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asleep in the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shades of brown. And grey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You 'bout done peeling them\Napples for the cider, Maud?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this one is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very interestin'\Nmethod you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I peel another?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,NO! I mean, naw...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's plenty\Napples in it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we taste it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,WOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best apple\Ncider I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Maud?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes like apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you she was\Nsuper honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're practically twins. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS AMAZING!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you won\Nthis one, Maud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really into "winning".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! You're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud is off looking for rocks,\Nso this is the perfect time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to set up\Neverything we'll need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to make our best-friend\Nrock candy necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? I'm not sure it's the\Nbest time to make best-friend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,rock candy necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, darling, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ever so\Nthoughtful to share
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,your special bonding\Nritual with us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, we've all\Nbeen trying real hard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to get closer to\NMaud, but, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe some\Nponies just don't click
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the way others do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wouldn't feel\Nright making something
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that means we're best\Nfriends if, well, we aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If anypony needs me I'll be in\Nhere trying to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do with 200\Npounds of rock candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel awful,{\i0}\N{\i1}just awful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have\Njust pretended
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we were friends with Maud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we didn't tell Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that we hadn't all become\Nthe best of friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Maud would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. But who really knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That pony is a riddle wrapped\Nin a mystery inside an igneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean\N"inside an enigma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I mean igneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a kind of rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me how I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come up with\Njust the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring everypony\Ncloser together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it Pinkie-Rainbow-Rari-\NTwi-Apple-Flutter-Maud
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It combines\Neverypony's interests
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,into one giant activity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can all enjoy together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will totally bring all\Nmy bestest friends together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as bestestest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, "Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably better\Nfor me to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Applesauce tunnel for Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, shiny stuff for Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading material for Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Critter time for Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes for yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a race\Nfor Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A rock slide, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For Maud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First you climb, then you slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad\Nfeelin' about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OH!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, goodness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, what\Nwere you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how important it is\Nto you that your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,become my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just don't think\Nit's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be best if I\Njust go back to the Rock Farm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and spend the rest of\Nthe week there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes me happy knowing Pinkie\NPie has such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never even got to make\Nour rock candy necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Maud. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Maud\Ncut her trip short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we\Nnearly lost Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to that ridiculous\Nobstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness Maud was\Nable to reach her in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see how\Nfast Maud moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way she smashed\Nthat huge rock into dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How in Equestria\Ndid she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pinkie Pie was in trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud would move mountains\Nfor her if she had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I think\NI've finally realized
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what we all have in\Ncommon with Maud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that just might be\Nworthy of a very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,super-duper special tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that only the closest and\Nbestest of friends can share.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for\Ncoming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long I'll be\Ngone on my rock research trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I still get to spend\Nsome time with you before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I put so much\Npressure on everypony to bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted my friends to get\Nto know my amazing older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, we're so sorry\Nwe hurt your feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,by not bonding with\NMaud right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And Maud, we're sorry that\Nyou felt the only way to spare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie's feelings was\Nto leave Ponyville early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen how much you care\Nabout Pinkie Pie, first-hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie's happiness means as\Nmuch to us as it does to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're sorry we\Ncouldn't see it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that makes us click\Nand creates a special bond
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,between us is how much\Nwe ALL love Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty great thing to\Nhave in common if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you think, Maud?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, darling, I think\Nwe all just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd be a bit more\Nexcited about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her more\Nexcited in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you've noticed\Nbut I don't show my enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for things quite in the\Nsame way my sister does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're totally cool with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud, we'd like to give you\Nsomething to take on your trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you remember all\Nyour friends from Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to eat all the\Ncandy before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those all the\Nnecklaces Pinkie Pie sent you?
